{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these conditions there were indescribable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really without food, without anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Head full of lices.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember I couldn't get up when I was lying in the mud or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did try to just to sit down, I was just white for my eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were slowly dying, and around people were dying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I remember one date it was bombardment by the Americans and our [GERMAN] was near a SS camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the bomb fell seconds before and fell into our camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And afterwards, there were cases which I saw of cannibalism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, there were dead bodies all around, and the prisoners who were a little stronger took hold of them and one who--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the pieces of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw it as some of them tried even to boil it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say because I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pieces of meat, as food and they ate it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ones who had the possibility, they cooked it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of a very young prisoner who told me proudly-- was very primitive and there were many in the camps-- and he tod me, oh, look how lucky I was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was just some bodies in the [GERMAN], which nobody got it, and I was one of the first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I could take off a bit from the hips, which means there was still not only bones, but a little flesh left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was his great luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So people were starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only me there were many who saw it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw it with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see something which is looking like some pieces of meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were many other prisoners who tried to find some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
